latestPosts.caption: Starvick — where your vision becomes the theme.

An evening filled with divinity, devotion, and divine décor.
At Starvick Banquet, we had the privilege of hosting a soul-stirring Mata Ki Chowki — a night that was not just an event, but a spiritual experience.

Our venue transformed into a sacred space where every detail — from the floral arrangements to the shimmering lights — resonated with the energy of Maa Durga. The colors of devotion, the aura of positivity, and the power of collective faith came alive in every corner.

We believe that spiritual occasions deserve a setting that honors tradition and enhances the experience. And that’s exactly what we strive to create — moments that stay etched in your heart forever.

If you’re looking to celebrate a spiritual milestone, from Mata Ki Chowki to Jaagrans or Poojas, let Starvick Banquet be the place where devotion meets design.

Book your divine celebration with us.
📍 Starvick Banquet, Ludhiana
📞 +91-9732131000
